{"tid":295503,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"火影第三部玩忍界大戰，覺唔覺冇時間吸收？","createTime":"2017-06-23T20:44:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T03:34:14.000Z","uid":61443,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fef6aa46a397687cd23e813b531a2338af909b6b","tid":295503,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T20:44:23.000Z","msg":"我當<br />\n第一部 終結之谷打佐助<br />\n第二部 打佩恩 <br />\n第三部 第四次忍界大戰 <br />\n<br />\n第三部最大問題<br />\n要最短時間上火影課堂 <br />\n<br />\n生物堂：9隻尾獸都未認識晒<br />\n現代史堂：跟住即刻要認識其他四國人物<br />\n歷史堂：未吸收完咩，即刻再 bin c 學歷史英雄<br />\n<br />\n成件事就好似 DC 趕住出正義聯盟咁 <br />\n又想擴大世界觀又想介紹好多人物 <br />\n搞到個個角色無時間描述好空洞無血無肉<br />\n想講主題＜羈絆＞狂講又重覆搞到濫晒"},{"pid":"98a1b828efae90ed5073640c79470d65597d98e9","tid":295503,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T20:48:07.000Z","msg":"玩同死人返生對話<br />\n有＜羈絆＞ 感動到既 <br />\n<br />\n卡卡西 vs 再不斬+白<br />\n勘九郎 vs 蠍<br />\n翻版佐助 vs 佢大佬 <br />\n<br />\n得呢3個組合 <br />\n我係覺得有 feel <br />\n<br />\n就算係阿斯瑪果到<br />\n我都覺得冇咩feel"},{"pid":"ab77e01d391c6348f8f3204d3720d544ac7bb108","tid":295503,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T20:49:48.000Z","msg":"當然都係本人立場<br />\n人人感覺唔同 <br />\n<br />\n但係我真係吸收唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3896e75f6c278a23dba149611c79f83c752ce7e7","tid":295503,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T20:56:54.000Z","msg":"如果真係咁想玩忍界大戰<br />\n我會覺得當初留返個戲碼去 boruto 先玩<br />\n當然你編劇要鋪墊配合啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以參考下＜熱血高校＞<br />\n佢都係算第二世代先打全國戰  <br />\n成件事感受深好多"},{"pid":"5a28084ec536a0b46b8ea1f98e47164c9d4bcc34","tid":295503,"uid":41434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T21:04:34.000Z","msg":"覺 起碼要畫多一千話"},{"pid":"741d2dafb54f38ff742aa343517f1ca221d16101","tid":295503,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T21:17:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺 起碼要畫多一千話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢出左太多角色嗱<br />\n又要幫佢地搞＜羈絆＞<br />\n<br />\n黎黎去去2條橋<br />\n唔係死親人孤獨慘到仆街要復仇<br />\n就係你講返邊個邊個以前既一句感動到我<br />\n<br />\n佢仲要整咁多角色出黎<br />\n咪搞到自己無貨賣又平又濫"},{"pid":"1bd6f94e1afa561cb59c2c29eec8035312963aa7","tid":295503,"uid":19643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T02:06:32.000Z","msg":"我最想睇自來也"},{"pid":"52484ebbb632ac8c10fa9116a23f43e859a80bed","tid":295503,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T02:48:14.000Z","msg":"廉價劇情  推堆人出黎純過場"},{"pid":"42801ed50d841617f6f5598aefb312eb6b41958a","tid":295503,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:56:22.000Z","msg":"其實係＜穢土轉生＞破壞左火影先岩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9add30d8957c16f5589eacaddacb79c656ef8a1c","tid":295503,"uid":1861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:10:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係＜穢土轉生＞破壞左火影先岩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n話穢土轉生破壞左火影既論據究竟係咩？<br />\n定你expect只靠一堆白絕去打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bc42563b2306d0b54f807a8135db36957d93bb","tid":295503,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:35:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實係＜穢土轉生＞破壞左火影先岩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n話穢土轉生破壞左火影既論據究竟係咩？<br />\n定你expect只靠一堆白絕去打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢整返啲歷史英雄出黎<br />\n跟住咪又要講一大堆 ＜羈絆＞ 囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef69868fa65fd90c17e64a6518f7609e063e051","tid":295503,"uid":104941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:34:14.000Z","msg":"忍界大戰好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打咁耐 去到最尾已經係怪獸打怪獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dea